vim: ft=markdownlight

Formats:
- ini
- json / json5 (=json + comments)
- yaml
  Pitchfall: https://noyaml.com/
             https://arp242.net/yaml-config.html
- toml: https://github.com/toml-lang/toml

* Yaml:
- https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3790454/how-do-i-break-a-string-over-multiple-lines/21699210#21699210
- https://github.com/crdoconnor/strictyaml
  StrictYAML is a type-safe YAML parser that parses and validates a restricted subset of the YAML specification.
  -> https://github.com/crdoconnor/strictyaml/

* Templates:
- https://jsonnet.org/ (json + variables and functions)
+ https://dhall-lang.org/#
  -> https://github.com/dhall-lang/dhall-lang/wiki/Safety-guarantees#effects

* Divers:
- http://www.jsonml.org/ (=xml in json)
- http://jsonlines.org/examples/ (=json with \n delimiters)
- https://developers.google.com/protocol-buffers/ (serializing structured data)
